name: THE FIRST ONE
description:
At some point , some omniscient being goes out for a few days and forgets  his dinner on the balcony at home. From molds and fermentations of rotten food the Earth Planet was born.

This is an authorial photograph that records my first attempt to reproduce in vitro the creation of the Earth and everything on it. I believe that when I actually get it, this job will be worth a lot.
